    "description": "《Draft of Darkness》是一款建立在后启示录世界观下的Roguelike角色扮演游戏。带有生存恐怖、卡组构建以及资源管理机制等要素。选择一位生还者，构筑你的初始牌组，然后勇敢深入黑暗吧！<br><br>在旅途中，你将会遇到：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>与感染生物战斗，</strong>还有政府的机器士兵，以及其他生还者，与他们进行注重弹药管理的卡牌回合制战斗。<br></li><li> <strong>探索后启示录风格的城市。</strong>城市已被黑暗吞噬。地图均由程序生成，每场游戏都会不同。<br></li><li> <strong>招募你的生还者队伍，</strong>他们会在旅途中帮助你，每位盟友都拥有自己的卡组和能力！<br></li><li> 与商人交易，收集更精良的装备与更强的卡牌，也可以用这些来强化你的同伴。<br></li><li> <strong>管理黑暗等级。</strong>随着你杀死更多敌人，关卡也会变得更加黑暗和危险。然而，更深沉的黑暗也会带来更多的收益。<br></li><li> <strong>做出重要的剧情抉择。</strong>你的选择是推动剧情的钥匙。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于武器的战斗系统</h2>《Draft of Darkness》中的每张卡牌都要通过装备对应类型的武器使用。你可以通过组合多种武器类型卡牌组成牌组来制定独属于你的战斗策略。每一种武器都有其独特的机制，试着将不同武器类型进行组合，创造变态的combo！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/53e6db371fdaf34d7d8c9a1b5621e3c9.poster.avif?t=1761568213\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/53e6db371fdaf34d7d8c9a1b5621e3c9.webm?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/53e6db371fdaf34d7d8c9a1b5621e3c9.mp4?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索程序生成的地图</h2>找到新的盟友，抑或者潜伏在居民区阴暗角落里的敌人，又或者是隐于街道里的神秘阴影，甚至是被巢穴中的敌人残害的无辜生命。请管理好你的队伍状态，尽全力避免辐射与病毒感染！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/6bb2151008c6c29aa3bf0f9eb23567ce.poster.avif?t=1761568213\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/6bb2151008c6c29aa3bf0f9eb23567ce.webm?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/6bb2151008c6c29aa3bf0f9eb23567ce.mp4?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在黑暗中求生</h2>随着深入黑暗的地牢式地图，你会遇到感染生物以及其他可怕怪物。每次战斗胜利都会增加你的黑暗等级，黑暗等级越高，则关卡变得越危险。然而，从黑暗中幸存会为你带来更多奖赏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/bed52f88159968510d7260b0c107edc2.poster.avif?t=1761568213\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/bed52f88159968510d7260b0c107edc2.webm?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/bed52f88159968510d7260b0c107edc2.mp4?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每局游戏都有收获</h2>每结束一局游戏，即使你失败了，你也会得到信用点，用于打开卡牌补充包，为你的初始牌池解锁更多卡牌，为下一局游戏做准备。每次死亡只是一次尝试新战术的机会！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/f8b164ce6ed264440198f915d45449fb.poster.avif?t=1761568213\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/f8b164ce6ed264440198f915d45449fb.webm?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/f8b164ce6ed264440198f915d45449fb.mp4?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个选择都至关重要</h2>《Draft of Darkness》拥有独特的“元剧情进度”系统，你的每一项剧情选择都可以改变剧情的走向，提供新路线推进剧情。你可以在下一场游戏中尝试与这次不同的选项，但是请小心，某些选项可能产生严重的后果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/e814d4248e5d65276e297d3197122c14.poster.avif?t=1761568213\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/e814d4248e5d65276e297d3197122c14.webm?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380650/extras/e814d4248e5d65276e297d3197122c14.mp4?t=1761568213\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
